    <title>中国量子信息产业发展迅速，初创企业成为新兴力量</title>
    <link href="http://example.com/2021/04/21/company/startup-domestic/"/>
    <id>http://example.com/2021/04/21/company/startup-domestic/</id>
    <published>2021-04-21T05:00:00.000Z</published>
